# Pythagorean Theorem: a² + b² = c²
# Perimeter: c = 1,000 - a - b -> c² = a² + b² + 1,000,000 + 2ab - 2,000(a + b)
# a² + b² = a² + b² + 1,000,000 + 2ab - 2,000(a + b)
# 0 = 1,000,000 + 2ab - 2,000(a + b)
# 1,000(a + b) - ab = 500,000

